properties.Name: StoreDisplayShelf
properties.Description:
A storage device for small parts.   

Shelves-Board fixed horizontally and supported by a frame or uprights. May be of metal or wood. Shelves may be fixed or adjustable. Used for small stores. 

Storage locations on a shelf are divided into 'bins'.

Columns.Name: StoreId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Store.

Columns.Name: ShelfId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Shelf.

Columns.Name: SectionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Row.

Columns.Name: LocationAddress
Columns.Description: A unique address within a Warehouse that may identify a Building, Storeroom, Area, Aisle, Shelf, Tier, Bin etc.

Columns.Name: FloorLocationXCoordinate
Columns.Description: The floor location x-coordinate of the Shelf.

Columns.Name: FloorLocationYCoordinate
Columns.Description: The floor location y-coordinate of the Shelf.

Columns.Name: FloorLocationZCoordinate
Columns.Description: The floor location z-coordinate of the Shelf.

Columns.Name: ShelfLength
Columns.Description: The length of the shelf measured in the unit of measure specified by the Unit of Measure ID.

Columns.Name: ShelfHeightFromGround
Columns.Description: The height of the shelf measured from the ground measured in the unit of measure specified by the Unit of Measure ID.

Columns.Name: ShelfHeight
Columns.Description: The height of the shelf measured in the unit of measure specified by the Unit of Measure ID.

Columns.Name: ShelfDepth
Columns.Description: The depth of the shelf measured in the unit of measure specified by the Unit of Measure ID.
